content:
New and Changed Invocable Actions in Health Cloud

Create home visits and assign care resources that are manually selected by the scheduler 
Use the new scheduleHomeVisitsManually action.

Recommend resources to use when manually scheduling a start of care visit or recurring home visits 
Use the new getResourcesforMnlScheduling action.

Create a group visit and set the address for the visit 
Use the new groupVisitAddress and clinicalServiceRequestIds input fields on the existing scheduleGroupVisits action.
title: New Invocable Actions in Health Cloud Summer '24
